          "rabbiNames": [],
          "excerpt": "אָמְרִי לֵיהּ: חִיוָּרָא לָא עֲבִיד לַן",
          "endExcerpt": "הָאִידָּנָא",
          "summary": "The demons object that white substance is not currently produced for them."
