          "rabbiNames": ["Rav Chisda"],
          "excerpt": "אֲמַר לְהוּ: בְּדַקוּ בְּדוּכְתֵּיהּ",
          "endExcerpt": "לָקוּתָא הִיא",
          "summary": "Rav Chisda instructs them to check the place, citing his principle that black on white or white on black is a sign of leprosy."
