          "rabbiNames": ["Rav Chisda"],
          "excerpt": "אֲמַר לֵיהּ לְיָנוֹקָא: פְּסוֹק לִי פְּסוּקָיךְ",
          "endExcerpt": "פְּסוּקָיךְ",
          "summary": "Rav Chisda asks a child to recite his verse."
