          "rabbiNames": [],
          "excerpt": "אֲמַר לֵיהּ: נְטֵה לְךָ עַל יְמִינְךָ",
          "endExcerpt": "עַל שְׂמֹאלֶךָ",
          "summary": "The child recites the verse 'Incline to your right or to your left,' warning Rav Chisda to avoid the trap."
        }
      },
      {
        "startSegIdx": 2,
        "endSegIdx": 2,
        "fields": {
          "id": "0-3_10",
          "sectionStartSegIdx": 0,
